{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":960,"text":"For several years now,"},{"time":2400,"text":"we've been engaged in a national debate\nabout sexual assault on campus."},{"time":7160,"text":"No question --"},{"time":8400,"text":"it's crucial that young people\nunderstand the ground rules for consent,"},{"time":13360,"text":"but that's where the conversation\nabout sex is ending."},{"time":17040,"text":"And in that vacuum of information"},{"time":19120,"text":"the media and the Internet --"},{"time":21120,"text":"that new digital street corner --"},{"time":22880,"text":"are educating our kids for us."},{"time":26200,"text":"If we truly want young people\nto engage safely, ethically,"},{"time":31360,"text":"and yes, enjoyably,"},{"time":34080,"text":"it's time to have open honest discussion\nabout what happens after \"yes,\""},{"time":40680,"text":"and that includes breaking\nthe biggest taboo of all"},{"time":43880,"text":"and talking to young people"},{"time":45640,"text":"about women's capacity for\nand entitlement to sexual pleasure."},{"time":51440,"text":"Yeah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":52680,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":53720,"text":"Come on, ladies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54960,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":56880,"text":"I spent three years\ntalking to girls ages 15 to 20"},{"time":60720,"text":"about their attitudes\nand experience of sex."},{"time":63680,"text":"And what I found was"},{"time":65120,"text":"that while young women may feel\nentitled to engage in sexual behavior,"},{"time":69440,"text":"they don't necessarily\nfeel entitled to enjoy it."},{"time":73240,"text":"Take this sophomore\nat the Ivy League college"},{"time":75400,"text":"who told me,"},{"time":76640,"text":"\"I come from a long line\nof smart, strong women."},{"time":79920,"text":"My grandmother was a firecracker,"},{"time":82160,"text":"my mom is a professional,"},{"time":84040,"text":"my sister and I are loud,\nand that's our form of feminine power.\""},{"time":88360,"text":"She then proceeded\nto describe her sex life to me:"},{"time":91080,"text":"a series of one-off hookups,"},{"time":93160,"text":"starting when she was 13,"},{"time":94920,"text":"that were ..."},{"time":96400,"text":"not especially responsible,"},{"time":98520,"text":"not especially reciprocal"},{"time":100680,"text":"and not especially enjoyable."},{"time":103080,"text":"She shrugged."},{"time":104720,"text":"\"I guess we girls are just socialized\nto be these docile creatures"},{"time":108360,"text":"who don't express our wants or needs.\""},{"time":111560,"text":"\"Wait a minute,\" I replied."},{"time":113160,"text":"\"Didn't you just tell me\nwhat a smart, strong woman you are?\""},{"time":117000,"text":"She hemmed and hawed."},{"time":119040,"text":"\"I guess,\" she finally said,"},{"time":120920,"text":"\"no one told me that that smart,\nstrong image applies to sex.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":125920,"text":"I should probably say right up top\nthat despite the hype,"},{"time":128919,"text":"teenagers are not engaging in intercourse\nmore often or at a younger age"},{"time":133840,"text":"than they were 25 years ago."},{"time":136080,"text":"They are, however,\nengaging in other behavior."},{"time":139760,"text":"And when we ignore that,"},{"time":141360,"text":"when we label that as \"not sex,\""},{"time":144600,"text":"that opens the door\nto risky behavior and disrespect."},{"time":149040,"text":"That's particularly true of oral sex,"},{"time":151600,"text":"which teenagers consider\nto be less intimate than intercourse."},{"time":155520,"text":"Girls would tell me, \"it's no big deal,\""},{"time":158440,"text":"like they'd all read\nthe same instruction manual --"},{"time":161520,"text":"at least if boys\nwere on the receiving end."},{"time":165600,"text":"Young women have lots\nof reasons for participating."},{"time":168480,"text":"It made them feel desired;"},{"time":170200,"text":"it was a way to boost social status."},{"time":172800,"text":"Sometimes, it was a way\nto get out of an uncomfortable situation."},{"time":176560,"text":"As a freshman at a West Coast\ncollege said to me,"},{"time":179640,"text":"\"A girl will give a guy a blow job\nat the end of the night"},{"time":182400,"text":"because she doesn't\nwant to have sex with him,"},{"time":184600,"text":"and he expects to be satisfied."},{"time":186720,"text":"So, if I want him to leave"},{"time":188600,"text":"and I don't want anything to happen ... \""},{"time":192720,"text":"I heard so many stories\nof girls performing one-sided oral sex"},{"time":196880,"text":"that I started asking,"},{"time":198920,"text":"\"What if every time\nyou were alone with a guy,"},{"time":201200,"text":"he told you to get him\na glass of water from the kitchen,"},{"time":204200,"text":"and he never got you a glass of water --"},{"time":207560,"text":"or if he did, it was like ..."},{"time":211880,"text":"'you want me to uh ...?'\""},{"time":213920,"text":"You know, totally begrudging."},{"time":216000,"text":"You wouldn't stand for it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218960,"text":"But it wasn't always\nthat boys didn't want to."},{"time":221600,"text":"It was that girls didn't want them to."},{"time":224280,"text":"Girls expressed a sense of shame\naround their genitals."},{"time":227480,"text":"A sense that they were\nsimultaneously icky and sacred."},{"time":232320,"text":"Women's feelings about their genitals"},{"time":234160,"text":"have been directly linked\nto their enjoyment of sex."},{"time":238160,"text":"Yet, Debby Herbenick,\na researcher at Indiana University,"},{"time":241720,"text":"believes that girls' genital\nself-image is under siege,"},{"time":246320,"text":"with more pressure than ever"},{"time":248000,"text":"to see them as unacceptable\nin their natural state."},{"time":252560,"text":"According to research,"},{"time":253800,"text":"about three-quarters of college women\nremove their pubic hair -- all of it --"},{"time":258240,"text":"at least on occasion,"},{"time":259920,"text":"and more than half do so regularly."},{"time":263200,"text":"Girls would tell me that hair removal\nmade them feel cleaner,"},{"time":267360,"text":"that it was a personal choice."},{"time":270840,"text":"Though, I kind of wondered\nif left alone on a desert island,"},{"time":275080,"text":"if this was how they would\nchoose to spend their time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":278120,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":279680,"text":"And when I pushed further,"},{"time":281120,"text":"a darker motivation emerged:"},{"time":283280,"text":"avoiding humiliation."},{"time":285880,"text":"\"Guys act like they\nwould be disgusted by it,\""},{"time":288800,"text":"one young woman told me."},{"time":290880,"text":"\"No one wants to be\ntalked about like that.\""},{"time":294240,"text":"The rising pubic hair removal\nreminded me of the 1920s,"},{"time":297680,"text":"when women first started regularly\nshaving their armpits and their legs."},{"time":302200,"text":"That's when flapper dresses\ncame into style,"},{"time":304760,"text":"and women's limbs were suddenly visible,"},{"time":307360,"text":"open to public scrutiny."},{"time":309640,"text":"There's a way that I think\nthat this too is a sign."},{"time":312640,"text":"That a girl's most intimate part\nis open to public scrutiny,"},{"time":317440,"text":"open to critique,"},{"time":319160,"text":"to becoming more about\nhow it looks to someone else"},{"time":322680,"text":"than how it feels to her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326000,"text":"The shaving trend has sparked\nanother rise in labiaplasty."},{"time":330440,"text":"Labiaplasty, which is the trimming\nof the inner and outer labia,"},{"time":335160,"text":"is the fastest-growing cosmetic\nsurgery among teenage girls."},{"time":341160,"text":"It rose 80 percent between 2014 and 2015,"},{"time":345880,"text":"and whereas girls under 18 comprise\ntwo percent of all cosmetic surgeries,"},{"time":349920,"text":"they are five percent of labiaplasty."},{"time":353920,"text":"The most sought-after look, incidentally,"},{"time":355920,"text":"in which the outer labia\nappear fused like a clam shell,"},{"time":359680,"text":"is called ..."},{"time":361160,"text":"wait for it ..."},{"time":363240,"text":"\"The Barbie.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":364840,"text":"(Groan)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366160,"text":"I trust I don't have to tell you"},{"time":368200,"text":"that Barbie is a) made of plastic"},{"time":371120,"text":"and b) has no genitalia."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374320,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":376240,"text":"The labiaplasty trend\nhas become so worrisome"},{"time":379040,"text":"that the American College\nof Obstetricians and Gynecologists"},{"time":382720,"text":"has issued a statement on the procedure,"},{"time":385000,"text":"which is rarely medically indicated,"},{"time":387520,"text":"has not been proven safe"},{"time":389680,"text":"and whose side effects\ninclude scarring, numbness, pain"},{"time":395560,"text":"and diminished sexual sensation."},{"time":398560,"text":"Now, admittedly,"},{"time":400000,"text":"and blessedly,"},{"time":401600,"text":"the number of girls involved\nis still quite small,"},{"time":405200,"text":"but you could see them\nas canaries in a coal mine,"},{"time":408280,"text":"telling us something important\nabout the way girls see their bodies."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413760,"text":"Sara McClelland,"},{"time":415480,"text":"a psychologist\nat the University of Michigan,"},{"time":417960,"text":"coined what is my favorite phrase ever\nin talking about all of this:"},{"time":423320,"text":"\"Intimate justice.\""},{"time":426680,"text":"That's the idea that sex has political,\nas well as personal implications,"},{"time":430800,"text":"just like, who does\nthe dishes in your house,"},{"time":433480,"text":"or who vacuums the rug."},{"time":435680,"text":"And it raises similar\nissues about inequality,"},{"time":439520,"text":"about economic disparity,"},{"time":441520,"text":"violence,"},{"time":442760,"text":"physical and mental health."},{"time":445120,"text":"Intimate justice asks us to consider"},{"time":448600,"text":"who is entitled\nto engage in an experience."},{"time":451960,"text":"Who is entitled to enjoy it?"},{"time":454480,"text":"Who is the primary beneficiary?"},{"time":457240,"text":"And how does each partner\ndefine \"good enough\"?"},{"time":461520,"text":"Honestly, I think those questions\nare tricky and sometimes traumatic"},{"time":466440,"text":"for adult women to confront,"},{"time":469000,"text":"but when we're talking about girls,"},{"time":471320,"text":"I just kept coming back to the idea\nthat their early sexual experience"},{"time":476640,"text":"shouldn't have to be\nsomething that they get over."}]},{"cues":[{"time":481560,"text":"In her work,"},{"time":482800,"text":"McClelland found that young women\nwere more likely than young men"},{"time":486640,"text":"to use their partner's pleasure\nas a measure of their satisfaction."},{"time":491120,"text":"So they'd say things like,"},{"time":492480,"text":"\"If he's sexually satisfied,"},{"time":494320,"text":"then I'm sexually satisfied.\""},{"time":496440,"text":"Young men were more likely to measure\ntheir satisfaction by their own orgasm."},{"time":502840,"text":"Young women also defined\nbad sex differently."},{"time":507920,"text":"In the largest ever survey"},{"time":509440,"text":"ever conducted\non American sexual behavior,"},{"time":512600,"text":"they reported pain\nin their sexual encounters"},{"time":516400,"text":"30 percent of the time."},{"time":519520,"text":"They also used words like \"depressing,\""},{"time":523120,"text":"\"humiliating,\""},{"time":524720,"text":"\"degrading.\""},{"time":526440,"text":"The young men never used that language."},{"time":530440,"text":"So when young women\nreport sexual satisfaction levels"},{"time":533840,"text":"that are equal to\nor greater than young men's --"},{"time":537440,"text":"and they do in research --"},{"time":539440,"text":"that can be deceptive."},{"time":541640,"text":"If a girl goes into an encounter\nhoping that it won't hurt,"},{"time":545280,"text":"wanting to feel close to her partner"},{"time":547320,"text":"and expecting him to have an orgasm,"},{"time":550160,"text":"she'll be satisfied\nif those criteria are met."},{"time":553120,"text":"And there's nothing wrong with wanting\nto feel close to your partner,"},{"time":556400,"text":"or wanting him to be happy,"},{"time":557760,"text":"and orgasm isn't the only\nmeasure of an experience ..."},{"time":561560,"text":"but absence of pain --"},{"time":563760,"text":"that's a very low bar\nfor your own sexual fulfillment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":569000,"text":"Listening to all of this\nand thinking about it,"},{"time":571240,"text":"I began to realize that we performed\na kind of psychological clitoridectomy"},{"time":576560,"text":"on American girls."},{"time":578360,"text":"Starting in infancy,"},{"time":579680,"text":"parents of baby boys are more likely\nto name all their body parts,"},{"time":583520,"text":"at least they'll say,\n\"here's your pee-pee.\""},{"time":586280,"text":"Parents of baby girls\ngo right from navel to knees,"},{"time":589480,"text":"and they leave this whole\nsituation in here unnamed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":592960,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":594320,"text":"There's no better way\nto make something unspeakable"},{"time":597800,"text":"than not to name it."},{"time":600280,"text":"Then kids go into\ntheir puberty education classes"},{"time":602720,"text":"and they learn that boys\nhave erections and ejaculations,"},{"time":606600,"text":"and girls have ..."},{"time":608360,"text":"periods and unwanted pregnancy."},{"time":612040,"text":"And they see that internal diagram\nof a woman's reproductive system --"},{"time":615920,"text":"you know, the one that looks\nkind of like a steer head --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":618640,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":622720,"text":"And it always grays out between the legs."},{"time":625760,"text":"So we never say vulva,"},{"time":627960,"text":"we certainly never say clitoris."},{"time":630360,"text":"No surprise,"},{"time":631600,"text":"fewer than half\nof teenage girls age 14 to 17"},{"time":634760,"text":"have ever masturbated."},{"time":637360,"text":"And then they go\ninto their partnered experience"},{"time":640200,"text":"and we expect that somehow\nthey'll think sex is about them,"},{"time":643920,"text":"that they'll be able to articulate\ntheir needs, their desires, their limits."},{"time":649480,"text":"It's unrealistic."}]},{"cues":[{"time":652440,"text":"Here's something, though."},{"time":654320,"text":"Girls' investment\nin their partner's pleasure remains"},{"time":657520,"text":"regardless of the gender of the partner."},{"time":660680,"text":"So in same-sex encounters,"},{"time":662960,"text":"the orgasm gap disappears."},{"time":666160,"text":"And young women climax\nat the same rate as men."},{"time":670120,"text":"Lesbian and bisexual girls would tell me"},{"time":672320,"text":"that they felt liberated\nto get off the script --"},{"time":675920,"text":"free to create an encounter\nthat worked for them."},{"time":679360,"text":"Gay girls also challenged\nthe idea of first intercourse"},{"time":683040,"text":"as the definition of virginity."},{"time":685000,"text":"Not because intercourse isn't a big deal,"},{"time":687600,"text":"but it's worth questioning\nwhy we consider this one act,"},{"time":692000,"text":"which most girls associate\nwith discomfort or pain,"},{"time":694840,"text":"to be the line in the sand\nof sexual adulthood --"},{"time":698360,"text":"so much more meaningful,"},{"time":699840,"text":"so much more transformative\nthan anything else."},{"time":703640,"text":"And it's worth considering\nhow this is serving girls;"},{"time":707120,"text":"whether it's keeping them\nsafer from disease,"},{"time":710160,"text":"coercion, betrayal, assault."},{"time":713600,"text":"Whether it's encouraging\nmutuality and caring;"},{"time":717360,"text":"what it means about the way\nthey see other sex acts;"},{"time":721000,"text":"whether it's giving them more control over"},{"time":723240,"text":"and joy in their experience,"},{"time":725680,"text":"and what it means about gay teens,"},{"time":728640,"text":"who can have multiple sex partners\nwithout heterosexual intercourse."},{"time":733960,"text":"So I asked a gay girl that I met,"},{"time":736520,"text":"\"How'd you know\nyou weren't a virgin anymore?\""},{"time":739560,"text":"She said she had to Google it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":741040,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":743240,"text":"And Google wasn't sure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":745200,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":747040,"text":"She finally decided\nthat she wasn't a virgin anymore"},{"time":750000,"text":"after she'd had\nher first orgasm with a partner."},{"time":753960,"text":"And I thought --"},{"time":755560,"text":"whoa."},{"time":757120,"text":"What if just for a second"},{"time":759800,"text":"we imagined that was the definition?"},{"time":763560,"text":"Again, not because\nintercourse isn't a big deal --"},{"time":765920,"text":"of course it is --"},{"time":767240,"text":"but it isn't the only big deal,"},{"time":770360,"text":"and rather than thinking about sex\nas a race to a goal,"},{"time":774160,"text":"this helps us reconceptualize it\nas a pool of experiences"},{"time":779280,"text":"that include warmth, affection, arousal,"},{"time":783920,"text":"desire, touch, intimacy."},{"time":787640,"text":"And it's worth asking young people:"},{"time":789880,"text":"who's really the more sexually\nexperienced person?"},{"time":793440,"text":"The one who makes out\nwith a partner for three hours"},{"time":796520,"text":"and experiments with sensual\ntension and communication,"},{"time":801120,"text":"or the one who gets wasted at a party\nand hooks up with a random"},{"time":804960,"text":"in order to dump their \"virginity\"\nbefore they get to college?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":809640,"text":"The only way that shift\nin thinking can happen though"},{"time":812840,"text":"is if we talk to young people\nmore about sex --"},{"time":816920,"text":"if we normalize those discussions,"},{"time":819280,"text":"integrating them into everyday life,"},{"time":822200,"text":"talking about those intimate acts\nin a different way --"},{"time":825760,"text":"the way we mostly have changed"},{"time":828560,"text":"in the way that we talk\nabout women in the public realm."}]},{"cues":[{"time":831720,"text":"Consider a survey\nof 300 randomly chosen girls"},{"time":836320,"text":"from a Dutch and an American university,"},{"time":838720,"text":"two similar universities,"},{"time":840480,"text":"talking about their early\nexperience of sex."},{"time":844280,"text":"The Dutch girls embodied everything\nwe say we want from our girls."},{"time":849240,"text":"They had fewer negative consequences,"},{"time":851200,"text":"like disease, pregnancy, regret --"},{"time":854640,"text":"more positive outcomes"},{"time":856440,"text":"like being able to communicate\nwith their partner,"},{"time":858880,"text":"who they said they knew very well;"},{"time":860600,"text":"preparing for the experience responsibly;"},{"time":863200,"text":"enjoying themselves."},{"time":865680,"text":"What was their secret?"},{"time":867720,"text":"The Dutch girls said\nthat their doctors, teachers and parents"},{"time":872000,"text":"talked to them candidly,"},{"time":873640,"text":"from an early age,"},{"time":875400,"text":"about sex, pleasure\nand the importance of mutual trust."},{"time":881480,"text":"What's more,"},{"time":882720,"text":"while American parents weren't necessarily\nless comfortable talking about sex,"},{"time":887520,"text":"we tend to frame those conversations"},{"time":890040,"text":"entirely in terms or risk and danger,"},{"time":894600,"text":"whereas Dutch parents talk\nabout balancing responsibility and joy."},{"time":900200,"text":"I have to tell you,"},{"time":901440,"text":"as a parent myself,"},{"time":903320,"text":"that hit me hard,"},{"time":905400,"text":"because I know,"},{"time":907960,"text":"had I not delved into that research,"},{"time":910240,"text":"I would have talked to my own child\nabout contraception,"},{"time":914040,"text":"about disease protection,"},{"time":915920,"text":"about consent because I'm a modern parent,"},{"time":918680,"text":"and I would have thought ..."},{"time":922000,"text":"job well done."}]},{"cues":[{"time":924320,"text":"Now I know that's not enough."},{"time":927920,"text":"I also know what I hope for for our girls."},{"time":931960,"text":"I want them to see sexuality\nas a source of self-knowledge,"},{"time":936240,"text":"creativity and communication,"},{"time":938480,"text":"despite its potential risks."},{"time":941120,"text":"I want them to be able\nto revel in their bodies' sensuality"},{"time":944600,"text":"without being reduced to it."},{"time":947120,"text":"I want them to be able\nto ask for what they want in bed,"},{"time":950360,"text":"and to get it."},{"time":952560,"text":"I want them to be safe\nfrom unwanted pregnancy,"},{"time":956040,"text":"disease,"},{"time":957280,"text":"cruelty,"},{"time":958520,"text":"dehumanization,"},{"time":960120,"text":"violence."},{"time":962080,"text":"If they are assaulted,"},{"time":963880,"text":"I want them to have recourse\nfrom their schools,"},{"time":967360,"text":"their employers,"},{"time":968800,"text":"the courts."},{"time":971120,"text":"It's a lot to ask,"},{"time":973240,"text":"but it's not too much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":975480,"text":"As parents, teachers,\nadvocates and activists,"},{"time":979560,"text":"we have raised a generation\nof girls to have a voice,"},{"time":984360,"text":"to expect egalitarian\ntreatment in the home,"},{"time":988240,"text":"in the classroom,"},{"time":989520,"text":"in the workplace."},{"time":991720,"text":"Now it's time to demand\nthat intimate justice"},{"time":996400,"text":"in their personal lives as well."}]},{"cues":[{"time":999760,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1001000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}